    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Places where medicines may be prepared on-site, dispensed, and or sold. Pharmacies are often sited within modern drugstores that sell a variety of products, though they may also exist outside of this context.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
